{"tid":2265140,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"最近鍾意咗個大我廿幾年嘅大叔，點知佢接受唔到我年齡……","createTime":"2020-10-31T07:53:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T08:07:17.000Z","uid":152123,"like":8,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1c135618203092d5105303ae03fdd02fff1dc201","tid":2265140,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T07:53:05.000Z","msg":"小妹今年廿幾歲，有排都未到廿尾<br />\n同個大叔（4x歲）關係發展得幾好<br />\n本來佢都對我好有興趣，經常有傾有講<br />\n大家都鍾意睇日本嘢，平時會講下idol同動漫咁<br />\n但我覺得佢好似一直都唔知我細佢幾多<br />\n對於我嚟講年齡不是個問題，我接受得到廿幾年差<br />\n於是有日同佢食飯個陣，決定鼓起勇氣同佢透露自己年齡<br />\n大叔=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，小妹=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<br />\n佢：你有冇去過xxx餐廳？以前好多人去架，估唔到十幾廿年前話執就執曬。<br />\n我：haha&hellip;&hellip;係咩。我就9x年出世嘅，間野咩年份執架？<br />\n佢：&hellip;&hellip;9x年？哦&hellip;&hellip;咁樣&hellip;&hellip;唔記得邊一年執呢？<br />\n<br />\n之後佢就面色一沉咁樣，成餐飯都冇再講嘢，埋單之後各有各行。<br />\n我個陣心諗，今次仆街啦，佢果然係接受唔到我年齡。<br />\n<br />\n第二日，因為我之前幫佢係日本訂咗某啲figure要拎畀佢，所以就lunch time上一上佢公司放低。佢公司好自由嘅（加上佢係高層，有自己房），所以我就跟住佢入咗去。唔入都還好，一入就知道真相嘅殘酷&hellip;&hellip;佢全間房都貼滿呢幾個女仔Poster同埋碟：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（右邊果個）<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2018/12/181203234805100707-450x300.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F181203234805100707-450x300.jpg&h=ad653ca7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.juksy.com/files/articles/52075/800x_100_w-56d9933887302.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F52075%2F800x_100_w-56d9933887302.jpg&h=544cb9c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.hkmarket1314.com/jkforum1583899615.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.hkmarket1314.com%2Fjkforum1583899615.jpg&h=1472ae9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（仲有好幾個我認唔到/唔記得名）<br />\n<br />\n我個下呆能咗，完全唔知畀咩反應佢，因為唔知道原來佢係咁執著於十幾歲嘅人。聽講最大果個都係01年出世。最後我默默放低個figure就自己走咗，我以為佢會問下我「唔食埋lunch先走？」，點知佢冇，就係咁我眼濕濕咁係lift口等咗五分鐘就走咗&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"56590727d071afde69ae10a444e6f6b32adc317c","tid":2265140,"uid":176282,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T07:54:57.000Z","msg":"0/10 冇是咁的"},{"pid":"2ba3838e08e595b8bdbcdc75d7510c3171d05b45","tid":2265140,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"56590727d071afde69ae10a444e6f6b32adc317c","tid":2265140,"uid":176282,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T07:54:57.000Z","msg":"0/10 冇是咁的"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T07:56:45.000Z","msg":"真人真事&hellip;"},{"pid":"eaeb024ca0d694b5a4249182fdc7961a18b3de5d","tid":2265140,"uid":113929,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T07:59:24.000Z","msg":"對佢黎講廿幾歲老啦，無咗少女味道"},{"pid":"8b70e4507a2f2def2b0af7f25a144ce36bf32bd1","tid":2265140,"uid":152123,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eaeb024ca0d694b5a4249182fdc7961a18b3de5d","tid":2265140,"uid":113929,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T07:59:24.000Z","msg":"對佢黎講廿幾歲老啦，無咗少女味道"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T08:03:33.000Z","msg":"本來佢唔知道我幾歲個陣對我好好的，點知當佢知道我真實年齡就&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"63f01233a6236032a0586e69260adc14af235d4d","tid":2265140,"uid":84668,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T08:06:24.000Z","msg":"個男人英文名係咪叫hunter?<br />\n佢應該覺得女人超過廿歲要人道毀滅掉堆填區"},{"pid":"f5c5d0372a25097b5dfeed458c0edde97eba2829","tid":2265140,"uid":152123,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63f01233a6236032a0586e69260adc14af235d4d","tid":2265140,"uid":84668,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T08:06:24.000Z","msg":"個男人英文名係咪叫hunter?<br />\n佢應該覺得女人超過廿歲要人道毀滅掉堆填區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T08:23:04.000Z","msg":"Joe"},{"pid":"67616c917df5e953894556c4faded815f106d247","tid":2265140,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T10:38:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\